              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/16723375/" class="">第39、40、41章</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/brightliwei/" class=" " title="追随我心1802">追随我心1802</a>
                (carpe diem)
              
